stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (THE TEEN BRAIN: WHY COMMUNICATION BREAKS DOWN) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Teens are not trying to be difficult. Their prefrontal cortex is literally rewiring.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (They need: autonomy, respect, privacy, AND your guidance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (Rule #1: LISTEN more than you lecture. Ask more than you tell.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (Rule #2: Side-by-side \(car, cooking\) works better than face-to-face.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (Rule #3: Timing matters. Not when they're hungry, tired, or in front of friends.) Tj ET
endstream
