stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (50 NON-INVASIVE CONVERSATION STARTERS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (\(Use during car rides, walks, or cooking - NOT face-to-face interrogation\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (   1. What was the best part of your day?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (   2. What stressed you out this week?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (   3. If you could change one thing about school?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (   4. What are your friends into that you don't understand?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (   5. Who do you sit with at lunch?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (   6. Is there anyone at school you're worried about?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.0 Td (   7. What do you wish I understood about being a teen?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 578.0 Td (   8. If you could have any superpower, what and why?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.0 Td (   9. What surprised you recently?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 550.0 Td (  10. Anything you've been wanting to tell me?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 536.0 Td (  11. What do you want life to look like in 5 years?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 522.0 Td (  12. What's hardest about being your age?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 508.0 Td (  13. Who do you admire and why?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 494.0 Td (  14. What would you do with $1000?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 480.0 Td (  15. Any topic you wish we discussed more openly?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 466.0 Td (  16. Which rule of ours do you think is unfair?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 452.0 Td (  17. Kindest thing someone did for you recently?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.0 Td (  18. What makes a good friend?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 424.0 Td (  19. Anything happening online that worries you?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410.0 Td (  20. Do you need more space or more togetherness from me?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 396.0 Td (  21. How would you describe our relationship to friends?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 382.0 Td (  22. What's your biggest fear right now?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 368.0 Td (  23. Is there peer pressure to do things you're uncomfortable with?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 354.0 Td (  24. What would make home feel safer?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 340.0 Td (  25. What are you most proud of about yourself?) Tj ET
