stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (SCRIPTS FOR HARD CONVERSATIONS) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (SOCIAL MEDIA & ONLINE SAFETY) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td ("I'm not trying to spy. I want to understand your world. Can you show me what you like) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (about [platform]? What worries me is...") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 628.2 Td (DRUGS & ALCOHOL) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612.2 Td ("I know you'll be around this stuff. I'd rather talk honestly than pretend it doesn't) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.2 Td (exist. What have you seen?") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 570.4 Td (SEX & RELATIONSHIPS) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.4 Td ("This might feel awkward for both of us. I want you to have accurate info and know you can) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td (always come to me.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 512.6 Td (MENTAL HEALTH) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 496.6 Td ("I've noticed you seem [tired/withdrawn/stressed]. I'm not judging. How are you really) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482.6 Td (doing?") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 454.8 Td (BULLYING) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.8 Td ("Has anyone made you feel small or scared? You won't get in trouble. I'm on your team.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 411.0 Td (THEIR MISTAKES) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 395.0 Td ("Everyone messes up. I'm more interested in what you learned than in punishing you. Tell) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 381.0 Td (me what happened.") Tj ET
endstream
