BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (This phone belongs to [parent] and is loaned to [teen] under these terms:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666.2 Td (  [ ] Phone charges in kitchen at night \(not bedroom\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 652.2 Td (  [ ] Parent may check phone with notice \(not secretly\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 638.2 Td (  [ ] No sharing personal info/location with strangers) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (  [ ] No downloading apps without discussion) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (  [ ] Respond to parent messages within 30 minutes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 596.2 Td (  [ ] No phone during family meals or homework) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 582.2 Td (  [ ] Report any bullying, threats, or uncomfortable contact) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 568.2 Td (  [ ] Phone privilege reviewed monthly) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554.2 Td (  [ ] Consequences for breaking contract: ___________________) Tj ET
