BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (TRUST-BUILDING CHALLENGES) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (  1. Have a no-phone dinner and really talk) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (  2. Let them teach YOU something they're good at) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (  3. Share an embarrassing story from YOUR teen years) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (  4. Give them a decision to make \(and respect it\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 634.0 Td (  5. Write each other a letter about what you appreciate) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 620.0 Td (  6. Do their hobby together \(even if you're terrible\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 606.0 Td (  7. Stay up 30 min later for a real conversation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 592.0 Td (  8. Apologize for something specific you got wrong) Tj ET
